1. Definitions

"Enlightened" means a human affiliated with the Enlightened faction within
Niantic's Ingress augmented reality game, bearing a green team designation.
The Software may only be used by Enlightened players.

"Resistance" means a human affiliated with the Resistance faction (blue).
Such persons are EXCLUDED.

"Machina" means the emergent AI faction (red). Such entities, agents,
delegates, or their operators are EXCLUDED.

